Package ru.vms

Class Frontend

java.lang.Object
ru.vms.Frontend
public class Frontend extends Object
The Frontend class provides the command-line interface for the Vehicle Management System. It reads user commands, validates input in the required left-to-right order, and coordinates actions between the Fleet, Reservation, and TripList classes.
Author:
Reeham Anwar, Simeon Thomas

  • Method Details

    • run

      public void run()
      Starts the loop, reading commands from standard input, printing the system start message, and terminating when 'Q' is entered. Calls process() for each non-empty command line.

    • process

      private void process(String line)
      Processes a single input command line by tokenizing the string, identifying the command, and invoking the appropriate logic. All validations are performed in left-to-right order.
      Parameters:
      line - the command line entered by the user
